1. install flask    -->   python -m pip install flask   --- ->from cmd
2. create app.py file
3. create instance of flask app
4. create route
5. Define methods for route
6. run the application

7. to display html page from flask 
    1. from flask import Flask, render_template
    2. create a directory named 'templates' inside the current directory
    3. Inside templates create html page (e.g. "hello.html")
    4.In flask function use below line to return html page
        return render_template("hello.html")